race.comment: MOLLY KEEPING (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fifth (20.63) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Has ability and looks hard to stop. SISTER CREEK (1) was seventh in a Grade 5 two back then in traffic and fell last time at this track. Must include in calculations. KUTA BEACH (8) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing eighth (21.17) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Expected to run well. MIA RED ONE (2) is worth consideration.
